                <h3>üí° Did you know?</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>**BNPL** stands for "Buy Now, Pay Later" - a financial service that allows consumers to make purchases immediately and pay in installments over time, typically without interest.</li>
                    <li>The global BNPL market was valued at approximately **$120 billion** in 2021 and is expected to reach over **$3.98 trillion** by 2030, showing explosive growth in digital finance.</li>
                    <li>Klarna, one of the major BNPL providers, was founded in **Stockholm, Sweden** in 2005 and is now one of Europe's most valuable fintech companies, serving over **150 million customers** globally.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

