                    <p>When a customer chooses BNPL at checkout, the provider approves the loan based on its <input type="text" class="gap-input" id="gap3" data-answer="underwriting" readonly onclick="fillGap(this)"> model to <input type="text" class="gap-input" id="gap4" data-answer="assess" readonly onclick="fillGap(this)"> creditworthiness.</p>
                    
                    <p>The primary source of <input type="text" class="gap-input" id="gap5" data-answer="revenue" readonly onclick="fillGap(this)"> comes from fees charged to <input type="text" class="gap-input" id="gap6" data-answer="merchants" readonly onclick="fillGap(this)"> for each <input type="text" class="gap-input" id="gap7" data-answer="transaction" readonly onclick="fillGap(this)">. Success depends on strong <input type="text" class="gap-input" id="gap8" data-answer="repayment" readonly onclick="fillGap(this)"> rates from consumers.</p>
